comments: Irving (DAL) places his off-arm against Holiday's (HOU) body as he stops and the contact is marginal.
Irving (DAL) picks up his dribble and VanVleet (HOU) never makes contact with the ball before Irving illegally dribbles again.
Jones Jr. (DAL) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Sengun's (HOU) right arm in order to get to the ball.
Irving (DAL) establishes screening position in Holiday's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the pick is set.
Green (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball as he contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot and incidental "high-five" contact occurs after the release.
Sengun (HOU) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Green (DAL) establishes screening position in Holiday's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the pick is set.
Lively II (DAL) is moving alongside Sengun's (HOU) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
VanVleet (HOU) steps into Irving's (DAL) space and marginal body contact occurs as Irving picks up his dribble.
Holiday (HOU) commits a take foul on Jones Jr. (DAL).
Holiday (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Irving (DAL) prior to any incidental contact occurring.
Doncic (DAL) avoids making body contact with Smith Jr. (HOU) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) jumps into Doncic's (DAL) body and delivers contact that dislodges him from his position during the rebound.
